<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Welcome to SpeakAnyWay!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .logo img {
      max-width: 150px;
      height: auto;
    }
    .header {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333333;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .content {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #555555;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888888;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="https://speakanyway.com/assets/favicon-76TnrIHG.ico" alt="SpeakAnyWay Logo">
    </div>
    <div class="header">Welcome to SpeakAnyWay, Vendor!</div>
    <div class="content">
      <p><strong><%= @vendor_name %></strong>, your business is now listed on <strong>SpeakAnyWay</strong> â€” a communication support platform that helps make the world more accessible for everyone.</p>

      <p>Your vendor profile has been created and is ready to be claimed. Once you claim your listing, you can:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Customize your public page</li>
        <li>Create communication boards for customers</li>
        <li>Generate QR codes to display on your menu, counter, or website</li>
        <li>Upgrade to unlock premium features and branding</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= @login_link %>" class="button">Claim Your Business Profile</a>
      </p>

      <p>Need help or have questions? <a href="mailto:help@speakanyway.com">Email our support team</a> anytime.</p>
      <p>Thanks for being part of a more inclusive world.</p>
      <p>- The SpeakAnyWay Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= Time.now.year %> SpeakAnyWay. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
